i est une actrice sud-coréenne. Sa première apparition a eu lieu dans le drame d'époque Mr. Sunshine et elle est surtout connue pour son rôle dans Tale of the Nine Tailed. Wikipédia","name":"Kim Yong-ji","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"金容智（朝鮮語：김용지，英語：Kim Yong Ji，1991 年 4 月 14 日－），韓國女演員。畢業於首爾藝術大學戲劇科，出道戲劇為 2018 年的《陽光先生》。2020 年在《九尾狐傳》飾演混血狐狸，其表現亮眼受大眾注目。\n\n國籍 韓國 出生 1991 年 4 月 14 日（30 歲） 韓國安山市 語言 韓語 教育程度 首爾藝術大學戲劇科 出道日期 2015 年 活躍年代 2015 年至今 經紀公司 BH 娛樂 代表作 《陽光先生》《Watcher》《所有人的謊言》《The King：永遠的君主》《九尾狐傳》","name":"金容智","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ким Ён Джи","primary":false}}]}},"person_2695385_translations":{"at":1772691652000,"data":{"id":2695385,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jaspers Lai Yit Hann (born March 7 1987) is a Malaysian-born Singaporean actor. Lai studied in Nanyang Junior College. Thereafter, Lai went to Hong Kong to be trained in acting, hosting, singing and songwriting when he was 18, and was in training for 5 years, along with Romeo Tan and Andie Chen. However, the artiste management company shuttered when he was 23 before he could debut. He returned to Singapore and enrolled into National University of Singapore, studying at the School of Computing.\n\nIn 2014, Lai made his film debut in The Lion Men. In the movie, he was cast as Sam, the leader of a rivalling lion dance troupe. He was selected for the role after passing an audition during his final university semester, and was also signed with Jack Neo's J Team Productions.","name":"Jaspers Lai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jaspers Lai","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","nam